  "title": "Delicate Smoky Indian Lentil Curry",
  "description": "A malty, flaky, and romantic Indian dish featuring smoked paprika and bonito-shave, perfect for a special occasion, this dairy-free-friendly curry is served in a lazy-susan-spinner vessel.",
